      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Wei-Lun Kao</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"/14th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"14th Computer Olympiad#ChineseChess\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/4/49/WeiLunKao.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:WeiLunKao.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Wei-Lun Kao <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Wei-Lun Kao</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientist, holding a M.Sc. degree from <a href=\"/National_Chiao_Tung_University\" title=\"National Chiao Tung University\">National Chiao Tung University</a> in 2009 on <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">automated tuning</a> the <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation function</a> for <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Computer Chinese Chess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. As member of the <a href=\"/National_Chiao_Tung_University#CGI\" title=\"National Chiao Tung University\">Computer Games and Intelligence (CGI) laboratory</a> headed by professor <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, he contributed as co-author of the Chinese Chess program <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chimo (page does not exist)\">Chimo</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wei-Lun_Kao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wei-Lun Kao</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>The Automatically Tuning System of Evaluation Function for Computer Chinese Chess</i>. Master thesis, <a href=\"/National_Chiao_Tung_University\" title=\"National Chiao Tung University\">National Chiao Tung University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ir.nctu.edu.tw/bitstream/11536/43333/1/553001.pdf\">pdf</a> (Chinese)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wei-Lun_Kao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=616\">Wei-Lun Kao's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wei-Lun_Kao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Wei-Lun Kao at <a href=\"/14th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"14th Computer Olympiad\">14th Computer Olympiad, Pamplona 2009</a>, Bronze for <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chimo (page does not exist)\">Chimo</a>, Image clipped from <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>TMSK wins the Chinese-Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#32_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 32, No. 2</a>, pp. 102</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wei-Lun Kao</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>The Automatically Tuning System of Evaluation Function for Computer Chinese Chess</i>. Master thesis, <a href=\"/National_Chiao_Tung_University\" title=\"National Chiao Tung University\">National Chiao Tung University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ir.nctu.edu.tw/bitstream/11536/43333/1/553001.pdf\">pfd</a> (Chinese)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsan-Cheng_Su&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tsan-Cheng Su (page does not exist)\">Tsan-Cheng Su</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Shiga wins Chinese Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#34_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 34, No. 2</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228151441\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in par